text:
The hot pair, who once weren't able to hide their attraction to each other during steamy PDA make out sessions all over the world, have been keeping a very low profile as they get ready to become parents.

As RadarOnline.com exclusively reported, Cooper proposed to Shayk with an emerald and diamond engagement ring, but those close to the couple observed his changed demeanor in the last few weeks.

Do you think Bradley and his pregnant fiancée's relationship will last? Sound off in the comments below.
title: Pregnant & Alone? Bradley Cooper & Fianceé Irina Shayk's 'Relationship On The Rocks'
